FlickrWave - A Flickr Gadget for Google Wave

To add this gadget to your wave, use "Add Gadget by URL" button and
paste this URL:

  http://github.com/schani/flickrwave/raw/master/flickr.xml

Enter your Flickr username or NSID and click "Go!".  To find out your
NSID, be logged in on Flickr and go here:

  http://www.flickr.com/services/api/explore/?method=flickr.people.getInfo

Your NSID will appear on the right under "Useful values".

For questions, suggestions, bug reports and feedback, visit this Wave:

  https://wave.google.com/wave/#restored:wave:googlewave.com!w%252BPY0VdPUkA
